oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bill Monroe Metal Photoplate Test
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Metal photoplates; Monroe, Bill, 1911-1996;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color card (black on white) featuring a metal photoplate of Bill Monroe with his band. This is most likely a proof or a test print made to check the quality of the metal photoplate.
